data.description: Come and see this AMAZING Open Concept! Northeast Clovis with 4 Bedrooms, 3 Full Bathrooms, Tall Ceilings, and an INCREDIBLE Owner's Suite Closet. Come through the tall entry way and be welcomed by a totally open Kitchen and Living area complete with Stainless Appliances, Granit Counters, and lots of storage. Don't miss the 4th bedroom that could easily be a second Living Area off the front of this 2536 Square Foot home!  You'll love having 3 bathrooms for guests/family and your own private getaway in the extra LARGE Owner's suite, complete with separate tub and shower and walk-through closet. Call today for a showing!
